{"product_id":"oreiller-soya-2-0","title":"SOYA Align Pillow 2.0","description":"\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eDiscover the SOYA Align Pillow 2.0 – The Ultimate Memory Foam Solution for Restful Sleep\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003eThe SOYA Align Pillow 2.0 is an orthopedic pillow made from premium memory foam, offering optimal ergonomic support for your head and neck.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eTailored Comfort :\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/b\u003eSOYA 2.0 adapts to all sleeping positions — side, back, or stomach — thanks to its butterfly-shaped contour that cradles your head and neck.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003ePeaceful Awakening :\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/b\u003eOver 200,000 users have already improved their sleep with SOYA 2.0. Say goodbye to restless nights — wake up refreshed and energized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eOrthopedic Alignment :\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/b\u003eIts innovative design ensures proper spinal alignment. The ultra-soft “Orthopedic Notch” at the center is ideal for back sleepers, while raised side zones support the arms of side sleepers comfortably.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eBreathable and Cooling :\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/b\u003eThe pillow’s breathable fabric promotes airflow for continuous freshness throughout the night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eRemovable \u0026amp; Washable Cover :\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/b\u003eSOYA comes with a moisture-wicking microfiber cover that’s easy to remove and machine washable.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p3\"\u003eWhether you’re looking to relieve neck pain or simply improve your sleep quality, the SOYA Align Pillow 2.0 is your ideal solution. Join thousands of satisfied sleepers and enjoy truly restorative rest — from the very first night.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SOYA PARIS","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53641794158924,"sku":"SOY_PIL_2.0","price":142.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0935\/5054\/3180\/files\/1-oreiller-soya-2_0HD.webp?v=1771634981","url":"https:\/\/us.soya-paris.com\/products\/soya-align-pillow-2-0","provider":"SOYA PARIS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}